put it on the roof.

344
00:18:49.798 --> 00:18:50.664
What?

345
00:18:50.699 --> 00:18:52.403
We think if we can
get it high enough.

346
00:18:52.438 --> 00:18:55.571
we could
broadcast a signal

347
00:18:55.606 --> 00:18:57.672
