00:24:18.291 --> 00:24:20.159
We're gonna start
digging up some new spots.

425
00:24:20.194 --> 00:24:22.425
make sure we are
constantly rotating.

426
00:24:22.460 --> 00:24:24.735
Let's not make it easy
