427
00:24:24.770 --> 00:24:27.265
Come on.
What do you got?

428
00:24:27.300 --> 00:24:29.135
All right.

429
00:24:42.722 --> 00:24:44.656
Hey.

430
00:24:46.451 --> 00:24:48.187
What are you doing?

431
00:24:51.489 --> 00:24:53.060
