Colony House raiding this place.

490
00:29:23.761 --> 00:29:26.333
-then it's gonna be me!
-Nobody's raiding anything!

491
00:29:26.368 --> 00:29:27.601
Well. those things weren't
supposed to be able

492
00:29:27.636 --> 00:29:30.975
