503
00:30:15.285 --> 00:30:18.121
Not as far as we can tell.

504
00:30:18.156 --> 00:30:21.091
There might be
resources out there.

505
00:30:21.126 --> 00:30:23.456
We go scavenging
during the daytime.

506
00:30:23.491 --> 00:30:26.162
never know what
